  "N_A_EMPTY_PORTFOLIO": "realized gross = 0: all cash; beta numerator = 0; normalized beta = N_A_EMPTY_PORTFOLIO; beta passes vacuously (no division by zero / no infinity)",
  "REFUSED_CODE_OR_DATA_IDENTITY:NAV_IDENTITY_MISMATCH": "construction NAV and execution-layer NAV differ within the order cycle"
